# My Dotfiles
My collection of dotfiles which fills my customized heart ï€„

The files customize the following applications:
 - i3 (specifically, i3-gaps)
 - tint2
 - rofi
 - kitty
 - fish
 - bash
 - polybar

## Required applications
 - python
 - pip
 - dotbot


## i3 Keybindings
`$mod` is `alt`

| Keybind | Action |
| ------- | ------ |
| `$mod+b` | primary browser (*brave*) |
| `$mod+shift+b` | secondary browser (*firefox*) |
| `$mod+p` | play/pause music (*mpc*) |
| `$mod+o` | next song (*mpc*) |
| `$mod+shift+o` | previous song (*mpc*) |
| `$mod+m` | open popup kitty terminal for music control (*npmcpp*) |
| `$mod+Return` | open kitty |
| `$mod+n` | open popup terminal (*kitty*) |
| `$mod+Shift+z` | lock screen (*i3lock-fancy*) | 
| `$mod+t` | open nautilus |
| `$mod+d` | open rofi |